This patch adds VSP device nodes for R-Car M3-W+ (r8a77961) SoC.
This patch is test on R-Car M3-W+ Salvator-XS board.

Signed-off-by: Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
